blogPost.excerpt:
A multi-agency investigation in Southern California led to the recovery of 33 children who had been missing, including eight who were sexually exploited, the FBI announced Friday. This story aired on the KTLA 5 News at 3 on Jan. 22, 2021.

Story: https://ktla.com/news/local-news/33-missing-children-including-some-who-were-sexually-exploited-found-during-multi-agency-operation-in-socal/

localize.title: 在洛杉矶县的行动中发现了33名失踪儿童。联邦调查局
localize.description:
美国联邦调查局周五宣布，在南加州进行的多机构调查导致找回了33名失踪的儿童，其中包括8名被性剥削的儿童。这个故事在2021年1月22日3点的KTLA 5新闻中播出。

故事：https://ktla.com/news/local-news/33-missing-children-including-some-who-were-sexually-exploited-found-during-multi-agency-operation-in-socal/

localize.title: 在洛杉磯縣的行動中發現了33名失蹤兒童。聯邦調查局
localize.description:
美國聯邦調查局週五宣佈，在南加州進行的多機構調查導致找回了33名失蹤的兒童，其中包括8名被性剝削的兒童。這個故事在2021年1月22日3點的KTLA 5新聞中播出。

故事：https://ktla.com/news/local-news/33-missing-children-including-some-who-were-sexually-exploited-found-during-multi-agency-operation-in-socal/
